prodNameC: 迪斯爾胎兒甲蛋白酵素免疫分析套組
ingredientsDesc:
Anti-AFP-Coated Microtitration Strips:
One stripholder containing 96 microtitration wells coated with anti-AFP antibody.
AFP Standard A / Sample Diluent:
Containing 0 ng/mL AFP in a protein-based (BSA) buffer with a non-mercury preservative.  
AFP Standards B-F:
Containing concentrations of approximately 5, 20, 100, 200 and 500 ng/mL AFP in a protein-based (BSA) buffer with a non-mercury preservative.  
AFP Controls:
Containing low and high concentrations of AFP in a protein-based (BSA) buffer with a non-mercury preservative.
Assay Buffer: (GREEN)
Containing a protein-based buffer with a non-mercury preservative. 
AFP Antibody-Enzyme Conjugate Concentrate:
Containing anti-AFP antibody conjugated to the enzyme horseradish peroxidase in a protein-based (BSA) buffer with a non-mercury preservative. 
TMB Chromogen Solution:
Containing a solution of tetramethylbenzidine (TMB) in citrate buffer with hydrogen peroxide.
Wash Concentrate:
Containing buffered saline with a nonionic detergent.
Stopping S
